      "visualDescription": "A cozy and heartwarming 2D anime digital illustration of a sunlit dining room in the morning. An elderly grandmother with soft gray hair and a warm smile sits at a rustic wooden table with her young grandson. On the table are steaming teacups, a plate of warm pancakes, and honey. Bright morning sunlight streams through a large window, illuminating dust motes in the air. The room is decorated with framed nostalgic family photographs on the wall. Warm pastel color palette, detailed clean line art, peaceful and affectionate mood.",
      "dialogueOrNarration": "It is a beautiful sunny morning today. Leo sits at the big wooden table. His kind grandmother sits next to him. She serves hot green tea and sweet pancakes. Warm steam rises from the food. [warmly] They smile and talk about their day. Old family photos hang on the cozy wall. Sunlight shines brightly through the window. Leo loves these quiet morning moments. Grandma tells a fun story from the past. [softly] Leo listens happily and drinks his tea. Breakfast with grandma is always full of love.",
      "subtitle": "It is a beautiful sunny morning today. Leo sits at the big wooden table. His kind grandmother sits next to him. She serves hot green tea and sweet pancakes. Warm steam rises from the food. They smile and talk about their day. Old family photos hang on the cozy wall. Sunlight shines brightly through the window. Leo loves these quiet morning moments. Grandma tells a fun story from the past. Leo listens happily and drinks his tea. Breakfast with grandma is always full of love.\nHôm nay là một buổi sáng nắng đẹp. Leo ngồi ở chiếc bàn gỗ lớn. Người bà tốt bụng của cậu ngồi bên cạnh cậu. Bà dọn trà xanh nóng và bánh kếp ngọt ngào. Hơi nước ấm áp bốc lên từ thức ăn. Họ mỉm cười và trò chuyện về ngày mới. Những bức ảnh gia đình cũ treo trên bức tường ấm cúng. Ánh nắng mặt trời chiếu sáng rực rỡ qua cửa sổ. Leo yêu thích những khoảnh khắc buổi sáng yên bình này. Bà kể một câu chuyện vui từ ngày xưa. Leo vui vẻ lắng nghe và uống trà. Bữa sáng với bà luôn ngập tràn tình yêu thương.",
